---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Ambit Accounting & Bookkeeping" description="Ambit — your trusted accounting and bookkeeping partner for US, UK, and UAE businesses. 12+ years of experience, 280+ clients, and a mission to simplify finance.">
  <Navbar />

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section
    class="relative min-h-[88vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden"
    style="background-color: #0F172A;"
    x-data="{ visible: false }"
    x-init="setTimeout(() => visible = true, 100)"
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600880292203-757bb62b4baf?w=1800&q=80"
        alt="Ambit team"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        style="opacity: 0.15;"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #0F172A 45%, #1a4480 100%); opacity: 0.9;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute top-20 right-24 w-96 h-96 rounded-full blur-3xl" style="background: #1a4480; opacity: 0.12;"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-16 w-72 h-72 rounded-full blur-3xl" style="background: #3B82F6; opacity: 0.07;"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-32 text-center">

      <div
        x-show="visible"
        x-transition:enter="transition duration-700"
        x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-y-4"
        x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8"
        style="background-color: #1E293B; color: #94A3B8; border: 1px solid #334155;"
      >
        <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" style="color: #1a4480;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-2 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/></svg>
        About Ambit
      </div>

      <h1
        x-show="visible"
        x-transition:enter="transition duration-700 delay-100"
        x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 translate-y-6"
        x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0"
        class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-black leading-none mb-8 text-white"
        style="letter-spacing: -0.03em;"
      >
        20+ Years Supporting <br />
        <span style="color: #3B82F6;">&amp; the Structure Behind</span><br />
         Growing Businesses
      </h1>
      <p
        x-show="visible"
        x-transition:enter="transition duration-700 delay-200"
        x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 translate-y-4"
        x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0"
        class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto"
        style="color: #94A3B8;"
      >
        As businesses scale, complexity increases across teams, systems, and reporting. Without structure, this quickly becomes difficult to manage.
Ambit brings alignment across these moving parts, ensuring that operations remain controlled and dependable.

      </p>

      <div
        x-show="visible"
        x-transition:enter="transition duration-700 delay-300"
        x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 translate-y-4"
        x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0"
        class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-16"
      >
        <a href="/contact" class="px-8 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-white rounded-lg transition-all hover:opacity-90 hover:scale-105" style="background-color: #1a4480;">
          Book Free Consultation
        </a>
        <a href="#our-story" class="px-8 py-4 text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg border transition-all hover:bg-white/5" style="color: #94A3B8; border-color: #334155;">
          Our Story
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats row -->
      <div
        x-show="visible"
        x-transition:enter="transition duration-700 delay-400"
        x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0"
        x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100"
        class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto pt-12 border-t"
        style="border-color: #1E293B;"
      >
        {[
          { val: '500+', label: 'Clients' },
          { val: '20+', label: 'Years' },
          { val: '250+', label: 'Staff' },
          { val: '3', label: 'Markets' },
        ].map(({ val, label }) => (
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-1">{val}</div>
            <div class="text-xs" style="color: #64748B;">{label}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
 
  <!-- ===== TRUST STRIP ===== -->
  <div class="w-full py-4 overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #1a4480;">
    <div class="flex gap-12 items-center" style="animation: marquee 30s linear infinite; width: max-content;">
      {[
        '✔ 20+ Years Experience',
        '✔ 500+ Clients',
        '✔ 250+ Professionals',
        '✔ UK · US · UAE Presence',
        '✔ ISO 27001 Certified',
        '✔ GDPR Compliant',
        '✔ ICO Registered',
        '✔ UK & US GAAP Standards',
        '✔ 20+ Years Experience',
        '✔ 500+ Clients',
        '✔ 250+ Professionals',
        '✔ UK · US · UAE Presence',
        '✔ ISO 27001 Certified',
        '✔ GDPR Compliant',
        '✔ ICO Registered',
        '✔ UK & US GAAP Standards',
      ].map(item => (
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-white whitespace-nowrap">{item}</span>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== OUR STORY ===== -->
  <section id="our-story" class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7?w=800&q=80"
            alt="Ambit team collaboration"
            class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-xl"
          />
          <div class="absolute top-6 -right-6 px-5 py-4 rounded-xl shadow-xl" style="background-color: #0F172A;">
            <div class="text-2xl font-black" style="color: #3B82F6;">2004</div>
            <div class="text-xs" style="color: #64748B;">Established</div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 -left-6 px-5 py-4 rounded-xl shadow-xl" style="background-color: #0F172A;">
            <div class="text-2xl font-black" style="color: #22C55E;">500+</div>
            <div class="text-xs" style="color: #64748B;">Clients Served</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4" style="color: #1a4480;">Who We Are</div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-6" style="color: #0F172A; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: #64748B;">
            Ambit was established with a focus on how work is actually delivered across growing organisations. As businesses expand, finance, operations, and backend functions rarely evolve in alignment. Systems become layered, processes differ across teams, and consistency becomes dependent on individual effort rather than structure.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: #64748B;">
            Over time, this creates gaps in execution, visibility, and control. <strong style="color: #0F172A;">Ambit was built to address that.</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: #64748B;">
            The firm operates across finance, operational processes, and delivery support, bringing these functions into a structured and consistent environment. Work is designed to integrate into existing systems and workflows, ensuring <strong style="color: #0F172A;">continuity across teams, periods, and jurisdictions.</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: #64748B;">
            This approach has been applied across businesses and professional firms operating in the <strong style="color: #0F172A;">United Kingdom, United States, and the United Arab Emirates.</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">
            The objective is not simply to complete work, but to ensure that it holds without rework, reinterpretation, or dependency on constant oversight.
          </p>

          <!-- Country flags -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-10">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest" style="color: #64748B;">Serving</span>
            {[
              { flag: 'gb', label: 'UK' },
              { flag: 'us', label: 'USA' },
              { flag: 'ae', label: 'UAE' },
            ].map(({ flag, label }) => (
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg" style="background-color: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;">
                <img src={`https://flagcdn.com/w20/${flag}.png`} alt={label} class="w-5 h-3.5 object-cover rounded-sm" />
                <span class="text-xs font-semibold" style="color: #374151;">{label}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== MISSION & VISION ===== -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12" style="background-color: #F8FAFC;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-stretch">

        <!-- Mission -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col" style="padding: 2.5rem;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6" style="background-color: #EFF6FF;">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #1a4480;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: #1a4480;">Our Mission</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #0F172A;">Structure. Consistency. Control.</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">
            To structure and manage financial and operational workflows in a way that remains consistent across systems, teams, and jurisdictions.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mt-4" style="color: #64748B;">
            The focus is on ensuring that work integrates cleanly into existing environments, maintains continuity over time, and does not require repeated correction or interpretation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Vision -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl flex flex-col" style="background-color: #0F172A; padding: 2.5rem;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6" style="background-color: #1E293B;">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #3B82F6;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: #64748B;">Our Vision</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 text-white">Aligned. Controlled. Scalable.</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-8" style="color: #94A3B8;">
            To build a firm where finance, operations, and delivery functions are aligned, controlled, and able to scale without breakdown across markets.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-8 border-t mt-auto" style="border-color: #1E293B;">
            {[
              { val: '20+', label: 'Years of Experience' },
              { val: '500+', label: 'Clients Supported' },
              { val: '250+', label: 'Professionals' },
            ].map(({ val, label }) => (
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-black mb-1" style="color: #3B82F6;">{val}</div>
                <div class="text-xs" style="color: #64748B;">{label}</div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== WHY AMBIT ===== -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: #1a4480;">Why Choose Us</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #0F172A; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">Why Ambit</h2>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: #64748B;">
          Financial work rarely fails at the task level. The issue is usually how it is structured, reviewed, and maintained over time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          {
            icon: 'M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z',
            title: 'Structured Delivery',
            desc: 'Work is aligned to existing systems and workflows, not layered on top of them.',
          },
          {
            icon: 'M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15',
            title: 'Consistency Across Engagements',
            desc: 'Outputs remain uniform across teams, periods, and jurisdictions without dependency on rework.',
          },
          {
            icon: 'M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z',
            title: 'Control Built Into Process',
            desc: 'Clear review layers and defined workflows ensure reliability as volume and complexity increase.',
          },
          {
            icon: 'M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z',
            title: 'Integrated Approach',
            desc: 'Finance, operational support, and delivery functions are managed as connected components.',
          },
          {
            icon: 'M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z',
            title: 'Scalable Capacity',
            desc: 'Teams expand in line with requirements without increasing internal complexity.',
          },
          {
            icon: 'M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z',
            title: 'Security and Governance',
            desc: 'Controlled environments with defined access, supported by ISO 27001 standards and GDPR-aligned practices.',
          },
        ].map(({ icon, title, desc }) => (
          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-100 transition-all" style="background-color: #FAFAFA;">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5" style="background-color: #EFF6FF;">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #1a4480;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d={icon} />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0F172A;">{title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">{desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

    
  <!-- ===== OUR TEAM ===== -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12" style="background-color: #F8FAFC;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: #1a4480;">Leadership</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #0F172A; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">People Behind Ambit</h2>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: #64748B;">
          A team of professionals working across finance, operations, and delivery, supporting businesses and firms operating across multiple jurisdictions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Nishant Sharma -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg mb-8" style="background-color: #0F172A; border: 1px solid #1E293B;">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="relative" style="min-height: 480px;">
            <img
              src="/images/nishant.jpg"
              alt="Nishant Sharma"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
              style="position: absolute; inset: 0; height: 100%;"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 60%, #0F172A 100%);"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 lg:hidden">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest" style="background-color: #1a4480; color: white;">Founder & CEO</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col justify-center" style="padding: 3rem;">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest inline-block mb-6 self-start" style="background-color: #1a4480; color: white;">Founder & CEO</span>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-2" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">Nishant Sharma</h3>
            <div class="text-sm mb-1" style="color: #3B82F6;">Founder & Chief Executive Officer</div>
            <div class="text-xs mb-6" style="color: #475569;">Chartered Accountant · Profit First Professional (Advanced)</div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: #94A3B8;">
              Nishant brings over 20 years of experience across accounting, financial operations, and advisory, working with businesses and professional firms across the United Kingdom, United States, and the United Arab Emirates.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: #94A3B8;">
              His work has focused on structuring financial and operational systems so that they remain consistent under scale — aligning workflows, improving reporting reliability, and ensuring that delivery integrates cleanly into how organisations operate.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: #94A3B8;">
              His approach is grounded in a simple principle.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm italic mb-8" style="color: #64748B;">
              "Financial and operational systems should not depend on constant interpretation to function effectively."
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-6 border-t" style="border-color: #1E293B;">
              {[
                { val: '20+', label: 'Years Experience' },
                { val: '500+', label: 'Clients Supported' },
                { val: '3', label: 'Markets Covered' },
              ].map(({ val, label }) => (
                <div>
                  <div class="text-2xl font-black mb-1" style="color: #3B82F6;">{val}</div>
                  <div class="text-xs" style="color: #64748B;">{label}</div>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Greg Johnson -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg mb-8" style="background-color: #0F172A; border: 1px solid #1E293B;">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="relative" style="min-height: 420px;">
            <img
              src="/images/greg.jpg"
              alt="Greg Johnson"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
              style="position: absolute; inset: 0; height: 100%;"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 60%, #0F172A 100%);"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 lg:hidden">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest" style="background-color: #1a4480; color: white;">Co-Founder & Tax Advisor</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col justify-center" style="padding: 3rem;">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest inline-block mb-6 self-start" style="background-color: #1a4480; color: white;">Co-Founder & Tax Advisor</span>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-2" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">Greg Johnson, CPA</h3>
            <div class="text-sm mb-1" style="color: #3B82F6;">Co-Founder & Tax Advisor</div>
            <div class="text-xs mb-6" style="color: #475569;">Certified Public Accountant (CPA)</div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: #94A3B8;">
              Greg brings extensive experience working with businesses and professional practices across the United States, Canada, Europe, and Australia.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: #94A3B8;">
             His work spans financial analysis, tax strategy, and operational performance, with a focus on helping businesses manage profitability and make informed financial decisions.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-8" style="color: #94A3B8;">
             At Ambit, his role centres on aligning tax strategy with broader financial operations, particularly for businesses operating across jurisdictions.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-6 border-t" style="border-color: #1E293B;">
              {[
                { val: '250+', label: 'Engagements Across Markets' },
                { val: '4+', label: 'Regions Covered' },
              ].map(({ val, label }) => (
                <div>
                  <div class="text-2xl font-black mb-1" style="color: #3B82F6;">{val}</div>
                  <div class="text-xs" style="color: #64748B;">{label}</div>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== HOW WE WORK ===== -->
<section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12" style="background-color: #0F172A;">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: #64748B;">How Work Is Structured</div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-white" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">Our Approach</h2>
      <p class="text-base mt-4" style="color: #94A3B8;">A defined approach to understanding requirements, setting up the right structure, and ensuring delivery remains consistent over time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
      <div class="absolute left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-px" style="background-color: #1E293B;"></div>
      <div class="space-y-10">

        <div class="flex gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="relative flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-black border-4 shadow" style="background-color: #1a4480; color: white; border-color: #0F172A;">01</div>
